New treadmill PR 🫶🏾 I hit my goal which was to hit 1mph unassisted at home by jan 1st!! And I did 5 mins without stopping! 

 If you watch, 30 seconds in I almost broke my ankle trying to talk but I bounced back 🦵🏾💪🏾

 A few weeks ago I tried this alone and almost broke both my legs and my back so my PT and I decided don’t go over .8 without the harness and a spotter! 

I figured it’s so easy at PT there’s no reason I shouldn’t be able to do it at home & sure enough! Lil mama just snapped! Lets gooooooo! 

#GAINS
🙏🏾💜 I am up to 1.3mph. I tried 1.5mph and I shouldn’t have. I’m happy I tried but no 😂

I legit almost passed out after this pic 😂 I was in denial while minimizing my closet & I was trying to convince myself this top just needed stretched out…

Nope! It cut my circulation OFF 😂 I almost didn’t realize until it was too late! My upper half got all tingly and started falling asleep & I had a lil panic attack thinking I wasn’t going to be able to get out of it quick enough 😩… anyways pics still cute tho 🫶🏾

I love that Cali is only a state away when I want a little get away 😍 my flight was only one hour and 15 mins.. Also this new hair cut is giving me life 🫶🏾

Don’t forget to clap for the small wins 👏🏾I ordered my sit to stand stick about a month ago and let me tell you these one handed sit to stands are no joke! 

The other day I experienced first hand what practice can do. The first time I stood up and the back of my leg didn’t touch my bed for support,  it gave me a glimpse of what is possible. That glimpse was all I needed…

And since I’m little miss challenge herself now I tell myself if I stand up and the back of my leg touches my bed frame then it doesn’t really count bc the bed is helping to hold me up ..so I tell myself ONE MORE until I reach my goal or my knees buckles- either way I finish 🔛🔝 bc I know I gave it my all, by choice. 💛 #healing #growth #mindfulness #workforit

Already hitting new milestones, engaging new muscles, and stepping out of my physical comfort zone @the_perfectstep 💚

💃🏾 Yesterday was my first time trying this machine where we did leg extensions and hamstring curls and I swear the hamstring curls almost took me OUT LOL! 

So at first I was uncomfortable with the machine bc I couldn’t perform the curls or extensions with ease especially with my right leg & my body was like WOMAN WHAT ARE YOU DOING TO ME LOL and I was asking Ashton the same thing!!😂 But she continued to push, coach and encourage me past what I thought I was capable of🔥 

I always leave PT feeling stronger than ever and ready for my next sesh! Shout out to my new PT’s Kristen & Ashton 🫶🏾 

I’m so very thankful for @the_perfectstep for sponsoring 10 PT sessions & for the @rollettes_la for always having the best raffles for your RE babes to win💕

#milestones #physicaltherapy #healingjourney #spinalcordinjury #legday #justdoit #duespaid
When you thought you didn’t get a full body pic, but you did 🫶🏾😍 #softgirl

If you get tight, sore, charlie horse or have muscle spasms after working out I definitely recommend using the Power Plate if you have access to one! It is such a muscle saver! Let me tell ya. If I go to PT & don’t use this machine after I am done then I am down and out for two days. Like completely immobile and crying lol for me this machine relaxes my muscles in a way that two days of stretching could never. By the time I am done with the 2 minutes I am sweating bullets bc it engages my core, my arms, my back and alllll of z leg muscles. 💪🏾 🦵🏾and it was really nice to have the spotters since i didn’t have my leg braces on and my right knee kept buckling from the days work out! 

And you can do it from your chair too! Just plant your feet firmly and press down a little on your knees to hold yourself legs in place and then you can feel the vibration through your hands!  #legday #musclebuilding #healingjourney#kotd #healing #sciawareness #growth #scirecovery
